==Translingual==

===Etymology===
from the surname Kalm

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Kalmia'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] at the rank of [[genus]]. This genus is placed in the family ''[[Ericaceae]]'' - North American shrubs with poisonous evergreen foliage and corymbs of showy flowers

